**6 files created/modified:**

| File | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| [gemini_keys.json](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/gemini_keys.json) | NEW | 7 Gemini API keys for Google Search Grounding |
| [api_client.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/api_client.py) | MODIFY | Added `call_gemini_native()` + `load_gemini_keys()` |
