**Pipeline flow:**
```
Character Pipeline → Visual Bible → 🔍 Google Check → Generate Prompts
                                         │
                                    Extract facts (code)
                                         │
                                    Gemini + Google Search
                                         │
                                    Parse corrections
                                         │
                                    Auto-apply fixes (AI)
                                         │
                                    Save corrected bibles
```

## What Was Tested
- Import chain verification: `ProcessController`, `ConfigSection`, `historical_verifier` all import successfully
- `load_gemini_keys()` correctly loads 7 keys from `gemini_keys.json`
- No syntax errors in any modified files

## What Needs Manual Testing
